scenes.description: Opening animation and title card for Gigi Murin's 3D Showcase.
Gigi introduces herself in a modern city setting before an accident occurs.
Gigi wakes up in a 2D-style fantasy town and encounters a horse-drawn carriage.
Gigi arrives in a 3D fantasy field and finds her fellow Justice members as cardboard cutouts.
A panoramic view of the fantasy town and castle as a song begins.

subtitles.original: I'm Gigi Murin.
subtitles.english: I'm Gigi Murin.

subtitles.original: I used to be 14 years old in 8th grade, but now I'm not!
subtitles.english: I used to be 14 years old in 8th grade, but now I'm not!

subtitles.original: I'm a bit clumsy, crazy and silly, and I may not look it, but actually, I'm a member of Hololive English Justice!
subtitles.english: I'm a bit clumsy, crazy and silly, and I may not look it, but actually, I'm a member of Hololive English Justice!
